headline: Lululemon Sues Costco Over 'Confusingly Similar' Apparel Products
summary: Lululemon Athletica launched a lawsuit over the weekend against Costco Wholesale, accusing the warehouse retail giant of infringing on its trademarks by selling clothing that is "confusingly similar" to designs trademarked by Lululemon.
